posting_body: ['Welcome home!', 'Schedule a Tour!', 'Book an appointment online at 2tour.site/OH9/NJQG', 'Creekwood Estates is set next to the Minnehaha Creek in Hopkins near shopping and dining.', 'Our spacious apartment homes feature central heat and air conditioning, large closets, and a balcony or patio.', 'We welcome pets, have a 24-hour Fitness Center, outdoor pool, on-site laundry, professional management, and 24-hour emergency maintenance.', 'Fiber-optic internet service is available!', 'Visit today and see why you will love to call Creekwood Estates home!', 'Home Amenities', 'Fiber-optic internet service available', 'Wall air conditioning', 'Balcony or patio options', 'Window coverings', 'Appliances in kitchen', 'Smoke free', 'Ceiling fan', 'Walk-in closet', 'Community Amenities', 'Pet friendly - some restrictions apply', 'Laundry facility', 'Additional storage', 'Fitness center', 'Swimming pool', 'Party room', 'Off street parking', 'Playground', 'BBQ area', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'Controlled access', 'Creekwood Estates Apartments Information', 'Address:', '1328 Lake St NE, Hopkins MN, 55343', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Details/?pid=6', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Application Fee:', '$45', 'Pet Fee:', '$200 - 400 (Note: Varies By Number & Type Of Pet(s))', 'Pet Deposit:', '$100 - 200 (Note: Varies By Number & Type Of Pet(s))', 'Office Hours', 'Monday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Tuesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Wednesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Thursday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Friday:', '9:00AM - 5:00PM', 'Saturday:', '9:00AM - 3:00PM', 'Sunday:', '10:00AM - 3:00PM']
